---
title: Spicy Lentil, Tomato and Spinach Stew with Herby Basmati Rice
description: The humble lentil is an exalted ingredient in French cooking with a texture superior to that of any other lentil variety. It has a delicious nutty flavour with a smooth interior and nutritional credentials to knock your socks off.
